'''Kuthyas Kawejan''' ( [[Sindhi language|Sindhi]] '''ڪٺيس ڪويڄن''' ) is a book on literary [[criticism]] in [[Sindhi language]] written by renowned [[Sindhis|Sindhi]] critic Mubarak Ali Lashari.<ref>http://www.thesindhtimes.com/entertainment/new-book-of-renowned-critic-mubarak-ali-lashari-published/</ref> It is published by [[Sambara Publication]], Hyderabad in March 2016. It is divided into two sections, Criticism and  Literature.The Criticism section contains fourteen scholarly articles  whereas Literary section contains eight articles on different topics.<ref>http://sindhipedia.org/Kuthyas_Kawejan</ref>

